{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"643949850e","title":"李先念接见卫生部部长及部机关各派的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7636b608c2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":9,"articleId":"643949850e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李富春","id":"25e2abfb25","type":"人物"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"李先念","id":"33f01f9c5a","type":"人物"},{"name":"黄树则","id":"b1ab2a70ef","type":"人物"},{"name":"医药卫生","id":"b55010d172","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c9d5a613f","type":"title","text":"李先念接见卫生部部长及部机关各派的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8def41e4f8","type":"paragraph","text":"〖卫生部几位部长孙正、钱信忠、崔义田、黄树则及部机关各派代表出席〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12b669c5e7","type":"paragraph","text":"李：你们分几派？","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8c0bedd71","type":"paragraph","text":"潘：有几个小组织没来，（指革联观点的）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"510ac85793","type":"paragraph","text":"李：我对你们运动不想讲什么，只想谈一点，你们要高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，要真正左派联合，不是和稀泥的。三结合必须是革命的、有原则的、不是和稀泥的三结合。对你们运动情况，今天不想听任何意见。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b511ca90b","type":"paragraph","text":"（李先念同志谈总理的指示：略）","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd15434741","type":"paragraph","text":"（信上还有李富春同志的批示：“今只谈防治问题）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0cf302d37f","type":"paragraph","text":"李：药进口，请外贸部解决。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"574c02d80e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：现在揪得厉害，北医八·一八把我弄到上海去十几天，后来医大又揪我十几天，北医又揪我十几天，医大也把我揪到天津去几天。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4692b0fb7","type":"paragraph","text":"李：马上开始工作，总理说这些人全力以赴，不要其他工作来干扰他们，在工作中考验他们。你们各个组织支持吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"262c891dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"众：支持。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"890b69373b","type":"paragraph","text":"李问孙正：你支持不支持？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9063a3a8e2","type":"paragraph","text":"孙：支持。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dda1cf5355","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：现在批陶大小会（共十几次）都要我去（只有一次没要我去）。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfbde3346f","type":"paragraph","text":"李：中央有好多条，要给检讨的机会，不要限制自由。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7e213895d","type":"paragraph","text":"潘：十三号开了个会（指革联）要他们（指当权派）抓生产，可是钱信忠和孙正策划假夺权，把生产耽误了。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50aed349df","type":"paragraph","text":"米智学说明了一·一七夺权的真象。钱、崔在李副总理面前互相说对方造谣，争吵不休。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"556fc62720","type":"paragraph","text":"李：你们今天讲的这些我都不听，我也不管。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1344506056","type":"paragraph","text":"（警卫员会后对红反团的同志说：你们老爷也会造谣。）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"100aae2b0a","type":"paragraph","text":"东方红郭义：需要明确一个问题，原来各司局抓业务，现在各派已各自为政，你搞的我不承认，我搞的你不承认，是否今后以卫生部名义，不以组织名义。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5282ec79d5","type":"paragraph","text":"李：对嘛！不要你说我假夺权，我说你新反扑。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a5041a962","type":"paragraph","text":"郭：（进一步说）那孙正搞的革命委员会不应该承认。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09bb34f7e9","type":"paragraph","text":"李：你们这个我不管，我也不说，哪些地方需要医疗队国务院就派医疗队。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd6e0ebc5a","type":"paragraph","text":"孙：明天要我检讨，今天才通知我，我来不及，甚至说否则一切后果由我负责，应该给我准备时间。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2fc0d3718","type":"paragraph","text":"李：是给时间准备吧！一天写一个检查都来不及吧！","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f31a9f4df","type":"paragraph","text":"孙：总理的指示我们全部执行，我有错误一定好好检查，但要给我准备的时间。今天他们（指革联、东方红）谈了许多文化革命中的问题，我不是用一句话、两句话能澄清，以后再谈。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61dcf6a314","type":"paragraph","text":"崔：防疫问题，是否由防疫司、药政局、医政司、财务司参加（崔的目的是想把这些执行机构拉入领导业务的机构中去）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2afbcf587f","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：我坚决执行总理的指示，我和崔两人轮流去检查，共抓生产。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7cd519985","type":"paragraph","text":"潘：今天总理指示三个组织来，可是孙正拉了四个组织来，欺骗中央。（李副总理根本不理潘，因为孙正在会前已将四个组织来人通知了国务院，上面同意后国务院门口才进得去。）","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e8c39fbe9","type":"paragraph","text":"李：文化革命中的问题你们回去吵，这些我都不管。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c8f5c701d","type":"paragraph","text":"东方红：现在抓业务有两套班子。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7aee17e59a","type":"paragraph","text":"李：抓业务，我只承认钱、崔的班子。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f00a649cf","type":"paragraph","text":"红反团：我们只夺文革领导权，对业务进行监督。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e3fa69e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"李：对的吧！","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dce9545217","type":"paragraph","text":"黄：我有许多困难，孙正、钱信忠没上班。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"336f69723a","type":"paragraph","text":"李：行了，你们文化革命中的问题回去吵吧！","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c061ef530e","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念同志拿了帽子就离开会议室。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff0e516067","type":"paragraph","text":"刊载于《中央首长讲话》（3），北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编，1967年4月。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"643949850e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}